        <p>International Justice Mission (IJM) India is a knowledge partner and collaborating casework organization assisting the law enforcement agencies and public justice system to rescue and rehabilitate victims of human trafficking. IJM also assists prosecution to bring criminals to justice. IJM India has supported the law enforcement to rescue 10000+ victims of human trafficking and bring convictions against 150 criminals from across India.</p>
